{"tid":1025784,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"飛機巨星吳京「包攬」中國影史上最高票房作品的冠亞軍","createTime":"2019-02-17T14:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-19T08:06:53.000Z","uid":41343,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a9dfd72fb63f7efc93680e4e35a641cb73b4d95c","tid":1025784,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"今天，上映13天的國產科幻電影《流浪地球》票房成功追趕上《紅海行動》，成為中國電影票房總榜第二名。<br />\n<br />\n目前排在《流浪地球》前面的電影僅剩下吳京主演的《戰狼2》，其票房高達56.83億元。作為《流浪地球》的主演之一、幕後投資人，吳京「包攬」了中國影史上最高票房作品的冠亞軍。<br />\n<br />\n目前最新票房排名（截至17日下午3點左右）：<br />\n<br />\n1、《戰狼2》56.83億<br />\n<br />\n2、《流浪地球》36.96億+（還在上升中）<br />\n<br />\n3、《紅海行動》36.51億<br />\n<br />\n4、《唐人街探案2》33.98億<br />\n<br />\n5、《美人魚》33.86億<br />\n<br />\n6、《我不是葯神》31億<br />\n<br />\n7、《狂野時速8》26.71億"},{"pid":"0671b3f691fe108c1406e4e4c2acc403ffa6e10e","tid":1025784,"uid":92,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:01:32.000Z","msg":"又要交稅了"},{"pid":"9c6f211bd92454d326cdd4293a8d0e40af3b76b1","tid":1025784,"uid":24788,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"頭3都係打飛機電影<br />\n吳京捉到路了"},{"pid":"ca7c8af6c369ed21e601b1f90080602735f49fa6","tid":1025784,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"男版泛冰冰"},{"pid":"40935143585b405afe2245a1dbe367dd6773f57a","tid":1025784,"uid":61271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"是但啦，支那啲票房水份咁高"},{"pid":"6d59219e9afe5cb41855d93a71cb2ff1f66ef434","tid":1025784,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c6f211bd92454d326cdd4293a8d0e40af3b76b1","tid":1025784,"uid":24788,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:23:24.000Z","msg":"頭3都係打飛機電影<br />\n吳京捉到路了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"開拍戰狼3 講打爆美國佬<br />\n即刻食埋個第三位<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c755d90be6df13700ae8b0fffd9